Package: doc.gov
Title: API Client for doc.gov (Department of Commerce - NTIA Data)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for U.S. Department of Commerce data via NTIA.
    Provides access to federal spectrum inventory data (225-5000 MHz, 5-6 GHz bands)
    and NTIA Digital Nation computer/Internet use statistics (1994-2023).
    All functions return tibbles.
